channel.title: The Hit List
channel.desc: It's a star-studded celebrity special, as some famous faces are put through their musical paces. The famous faces joining Rochelle and Marvin Humes in this addictively play-along music quiz are dancer Oti Mabuse and actor Catherine Tyldesley, rugby legend Joe Marler and comedian Maisie Adam, and comedians Chris McCausland and John Thomson. Who will get the chance to win ?10,000 for their chosen charity?
